        "subject": "=Issue I marked as resolved : {{$json.issue_title}}",
        "html": "=<p>Dear {{$json.project_manager_firstname}} {{$json.project_manager_lastname}},</p>\n\n<p>We are pleased to inform you that the issue <b>{{$json.title}}</b> has been successfully resolved.</p>\n\n<p><b>Resolution Summary</b><br>\n* Issue Title: {{$json.issue_title}}<br>\n* Resolution Status: {{$json.issue_status}}<br>\n* Resolved On: {{$json.updated_at}}<br>\n* Resolved By (Owner ID): {{$json.responsible_person_id}}</p>\n\n<p>Please review the resolution details. If you have any concerns, feel free to reopen the issue as needed.</p>\n\n<p>Regards,<br>\n<b>Issue Resolution & Quality Team</b></p>",
